        "default": "sequential",
        "description": "Message rotation strategy. Sequential sends messages in order and wraps back to the start. Random puts each message into a bag as many times as its weight, shuffles that bag, then sends one entry at a time. Weights only matter in random mode; sequential mode ignores them. In practice, higher-weight messages appear more often, but every weighted slot is used before the bag is reshuffled."
      },
